'''Amethyst Shipping & Storage''' was a phantom company on [[New Cov/Legends|New Cov]], established by [[Garm Bel Iblis/Legends|Garm Bel Iblis]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It maintained a warehouse in [[Ilic]], where [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] first met Bel Iblis' right and left hand, [[Sena Leikvold Midanyl|Sena]] and [[Irenez (Human)|Irenez]] respectively. Solo lost sight of [[Council-Aide]] [[Tav Breil'lya]] when he ducked into this establishment just before the raid on New Cov.<ref name="DFR">''[[Dark Force Rising]]''</ref>

{{Company-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
[[Wikipedia:Amethyst|Amethyst]] is a real world variety of quartz.

